-Hi, Louise.
-Oh, hi. Come on in.

07:47.535 --> 07:49.903
-Oh.
-Louise, what's the matter?

07:49.970 --> 07:52.706
Oh, I'm just sore from
too much dancing.

07:52.773 --> 07:55.175
-Too much dancing?
-Yeah.

07:55.242 --> 07:58.879
George and I have been
out discoing for the past
three nights.

07:58.946 --> 08:00.948
But I can't take it anymore.

08:01.014 --> 08:03.751
So he's going out tonight
by himself.

08:03.817 --> 08:05.586
By himself?
What's gotten into him?

08:06.353 --> 08:07.788
Disco fever.

08:18.966 --> 08:22.302
Well, who are you
supposed to be?

08:22.369 --> 08:24.538
Sammy Davis the Third?

08:24.605 --> 08:27.675
This is what the in crowd
wears down at Dirty Betty's.

08:27.741 --> 08:29.076
What's Dirty Betty's?

08:29.142 --> 08:31.278
My destination for tonight.

08:32.746 --> 08:35.182
See you later, Weez.
Freak out! Ha!

08:40.320 --> 08:43.123
I'm not sure I believe
what I just saw.

08:43.190 --> 08:46.694
Every night now
he comes home,
woofs down his dinner,

08:46.760 --> 08:52.332
and changes from
a conservative businessman
into a disco duck.

08:52.399 --> 08:55.168
Who was the idiot who gave him
the idea to start discoing?

08:59.506 --> 09:00.841
Me.

09:00.908 --> 09:02.743
Oh, I'm sorry, Louise.
I didn't mean that you're.

09:02.810 --> 09:05.746
Oh, that's okay, Tom.
It's my own fault.

09:05.813 --> 09:09.817
I told him
to stop working so much,
and get out and live.

09:09.883 --> 09:12.986
Hey, but maybe if we
went down there with you,

09:13.053 --> 09:14.788
we could try to talk him
out of it.

09:14.855 --> 09:16.423
Oh, Helen, would you?

09:16.489 --> 09:18.992
Hmm. You think he'd pay
any attention to us?

09:19.059 --> 09:21.528
Good point.
He never has before.

09:21.595 --> 09:25.065
Oh, Helen, please,
you are my only hope.

09:25.132 --> 09:27.100
Oh, what the heck?
Let's give it a whirl.

09:27.167 --> 09:31.872
Oh, thanks, Helen.
And if this works,
I'll owe you both a favor.

09:31.939 --> 09:35.643
Well, maybe you can get George
to stop calling me "honky"

09:37.978 --> 09:40.748
I said favor, not a miracle.

09:42.215 --> 09:44.685
-Come on, girl.
-Oh.

10:07.207 --> 10:09.777
* You set my lips on fire

10:10.711 --> 10:13.480
