10:20.187 --> 10:21.488
Oh, there he is.

10:23.123 --> 10:26.593
Yeah,
Mister Happy Feet in action.

10:26.660 --> 10:29.663
Looks like we'll have to wait
until he sits down.

10:29.730 --> 10:32.332
Forget it. He never sits down.

10:32.399 --> 10:35.035
Come on, Tom, let's go
talk to him over there.

10:35.102 --> 10:36.670
Okay.

10:36.737 --> 10:40.040
And, Louise, don't worry.
Helen will talk
some sense into him.

10:40.107 --> 10:41.541
I hope so.

