What you doing here?

11:13.874 --> 11:16.810
I came down here
to talk to you. George!

11:16.877 --> 11:19.079
-Hey, hey, you ain't
a bad dancer. Go ahead, Helen.
-Thanks, but...

11:19.146 --> 11:20.848
Get on down, Helen.

11:30.023 --> 11:31.424
Yeah, do it.

11:33.393 --> 11:34.928
Get down, girl.

11:43.971 --> 11:46.940
-Hey, Helen,
have you talked to him?
-Not yet, Tom!

11:47.007 --> 11:49.342
-Helen.
-Not now, Tom, I'm busy!

11:49.409 --> 11:50.410
But...

